        "TileImage": "$($repository 4b46ecec-89d2-4293-8737-e4c514024fff).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. Today you will return to China, Chongqing. This time we only have one target and a lot of information, so let&apos;s get started. Junjie Chang is a rich and influential loan shark. So basically he gives loans to poor people who can&apos;t afford to pay back, so that Chang can sue them and get the money. He may also have his troops beat up and demand money from customers, for example, our client&apos;s friend had to experience this, which is why our client wants to take revenge. Have fun!",
